    public class MultiValuedMap<K,V>
extends org.apache.commons.collections4.map.MultiValueMap
    An extension of MultiValueMap that supports generics method calls.

    The class MultiValueMap adds the behavior of adding multiple values to the same key. However, the API methods in that class support are non-generic. Hence this extension class is written with the intent to provide generic capabilities for most of the commonly used methods.
